{"tid":1352654,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"最近睇唔過眼想，幫幫香港人去英國打工","createTime":"2019-07-22T22:21:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T09:56:13.000Z","uid":147979,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"35f1cb53da9a85ab40ffa3a54b4a07438503b205","tid":1352654,"uid":147979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T22:21:03.000Z","msg":"大家好！我人在英國做嘢，呢排真係睇唔過眼香港變成咁，但同時覺得自己係英國好幸運。我唔知道各位香港人會唔會想嚟英國打工，但為左幫幫大家，我已經係英國揾左幾個香港人老細有工比香港人做。用Working holiday 簽證（有兩年時間，做得好老細可以幫申請visa 做長工），時薪最低有&pound;8.50。有興趣嘅<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">今日即刻</span></strong>tg我再傾！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/londongold\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Flondongold&d=4HHrVRRB2qdXUamIokVXjS%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=36205c3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/londongold</a>"},{"pid":"25f5b85bcaea673f37a1694622103056139356ee","tid":1352654,"uid":61499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T22:22:25.000Z","msg":"最低工資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eebd1f2254f9831e40534ea19d9835f8d3906318","tid":1352654,"uid":263150,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T22:27:06.000Z","msg":"個ID 名&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不了"},{"pid":"4fc3e3c7c8bd42dbadaee83b468189d87bb3ea88","tid":1352654,"uid":39431,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T09:56:13.000Z","msg":"簡單D嚟講就係呃人嚟做廉價勞工<br />\n<br />\n最後唔撚幫你簽T2，到期換過批人再呃過"}]}